---
title: Sweet Chilli Beef & Asparagus Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice
description: Beef that are popping with delicious taste sensations, we say yes please! You won’t be able to get enough of these bad boys in
a saucy sweet chilli stir-fry. Set off the flavour fireworks with ginger and oyster sauce stirred through.
